Naomi Campbell, 52, looked stylish as Spotify hosted an evening of music in Cannes, France, on Monday.The supermodel looked a fraction of her age in a chic ankle-length shirt dress.The garment featured a low-cut neckline and a belt to cinch Naomi in at the waist.  She styled the look with some chunky black and white Nike trainers, black sunglasses, and wore layered chokers and necklaces around her neck. While at the event at Spotify Beach, Naomi enjoyed performances from Kendrick Lamar and Anderson .Paak.